Opendfs Version 0.1

Introduction in Chinese you can see it in the 'opendfs.docx' doc.

If you want to change the release version, please modify the "PACKAGE_STRING" in scripts/version.

INSTALL:
    1. ./configure (default prefix is "/usr/local/opendfs")
    2. make
    3. make install

the "scripts" directory include some files of building system, you can change some files to fill your wants.

